---
title: Sriracha-Sesame Veg Gyozas and Noodles with Stir-Fried Veg and Sesame Seeds
description: Pronounced gee-oh-zuh, our Sriracha-Sesame Veg Gyozas and Noodles bakes the gyozas to turn them crispy and golden on the outside. Spicy sriracha, ketjap manis, soy sauce and honey make a delicious sauce to coat the noodles.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R41_W43_UK_R23728-4_Main_4_low_2-93d2fe69.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66c4866cac0a1f91a3671675-en-GB.pdf
cuisine: Asian
